nodes.name: benzoate:CoA ligase (AMP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + Benzoate + CoA <=> AMP + Diphosphate + Benzoyl-CoA

nodes.name: cyclohexa-1,5-diene-1-carbonyl-CoA:ferredoxin oxidoreductase (aromatizing, ATP-forming)
nodes.rxn: Benzoyl-CoA + Reduced ferredoxin + 2 ATP + 2 H2O <=> Cyclohexa-1,5-diene-1-carbonyl-CoA + Oxidized ferredoxin + 2 Orthophosphate + 2 ADP

nodes.name: Cyclohexane-1-carboxylate + CoA + ATP <=> Cyclohexane-1-carboxyl-CoA + AMP + Diphosphate
nodes.rxn: Cyclohexane-1-carboxylate + CoA + ATP <=> Cyclohexane-1-carboxyl-CoA + AMP + Diphosphate

nodes.name: benzoate,[reduced NADPH---hemoprotein reductase]:oxygen oxidoreductase (4-hydroxylating)
nodes.rxn: Benzoate + [Reduced NADPH---hemoprotein reductase] + Oxygen <=> 4-Hydroxybenzoate + [Oxidized NADPH---hemoprotein reductase] + H2O

nodes.name: benzoyl-CoA:acceptor oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: 4-Hydroxybenzoyl-CoA + Reduced ferredoxin <=> Benzoyl-CoA + Oxidized ferredoxin + H2O

nodes.name: 4-Methoxybenzoate,hydrogen-donor:oxygen oxidoreductase (O-demethylating)
nodes.rxn: 4-Methoxybenzoate + Reduced acceptor + Oxygen <=> 4-Hydroxybenzoate + Formaldehyde + Acceptor + H2O

nodes.name: acetaldehyde:NAD+ oxidoreductase (CoA-acetylating)
nodes.rxn: Acetaldehyde + CoA + NAD+ <=> Acetyl-CoA + NADH + H+

nodes.name: benzene,NADH:oxygene 1,2-oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Benzene + Oxygen + NADH + H+ <=> cis-1,2-Dihydrobenzene-1,2-diol + NAD+

nodes.name: benzene,NADH:oxygen oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Benzene + Oxygen + NADH + H+ <=> Phenol + NAD+ + H2O

nodes.name: phenol,NADH:oxygen oxidoreductase (2-hydroxylating)
nodes.rxn: Phenol + Oxygen + NADH + H+ <=> Catechol + NAD+ + H2O

nodes.name: cyclohex-1-ene-1-carbonyl-CoA:electron transfer flavoprotein oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Cyclohex-1-ene-1-carboxyl-CoA + Electron-transferring flavoprotein <=> Cyclohexa-1,5-diene-1-carbonyl-CoA + Reduced electron-transferring flavoprotein

nodes.name: cyclohexane-1-carbonyl-CoA:electron transfer flavoprotein oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Cyclohexane-1-carboxyl-CoA + Electron-transferring flavoprotein <=> Cyclohex-1-ene-1-carboxyl-CoA + Reduced electron-transferring flavoprotein

nodes.name: glutaryl-CoA:electron-transfer flavoprotein 2,3-oxidoreductase (decarboxylating)
nodes.rxn: Glutaryl-CoA + Electron-transferring flavoprotein <=> Crotonoyl-CoA + Reduced electron-transferring flavoprotein + CO2

nodes.name: Resorcinol,NADPH:oxogen oxidoreductase (2-hydroxylating)
nodes.rxn: Resorcinol + Oxygen + NADPH + H+ <=> Benzene-1,2,4-triol + NADP+ + H2O

nodes.name: resorcinol,FADH2:oxygen oxidoreductase (4-hydroxylating)
nodes.rxn: Resorcinol + FADH2 + Oxygen <=> Benzene-1,2,4-triol + FAD + H2O

nodes.name: resorcinol,NADH:oxygen oxidoreductase (4-hydroxylating)
nodes.rxn: Resorcinol + NADH + H+ + Oxygen <=> Benzene-1,2,4-triol + NAD+ + H2O

nodes.name: benzoyl-CoA,NADPH:oxygen oxidoreductase (2,3-epoxydizing)
nodes.rxn: Benzoyl-CoA + NADPH + H+ + Oxygen <=> 2,3-Epoxy-2,3-dihydrobenzoyl-CoA + NADP+ + H2O
